150
00:11:46 --> 00:11:50
 It can be told as your religion because every religion contains these three things only.

151
00:11:50 --> 00:11:53
 So swadharma means your religion.

152
00:11:53 --> 00:11:56
 There is no need of changing your religion.

153
00:11:56 --> 00:12:01
 You are born as a Hindu, you are born in Hindu religion.

154
00:12:01 --> 00:12:06
 If you die as a Hindu, don't change into other religion because there is no need.

155
00:12:06 --> 00:12:08
