175
00:13:29 --> 00:13:35
 And you will find complete unity in all religions.

176
00:13:35 --> 00:13:39
 If defects are removed, merit is one and the same.

177
00:13:39 --> 00:13:45
 There is God, fear for God, don't do sin, always do justice.

178
00:13:45 --> 00:13:47
 Then you will go to heaven.

179
00:13:47 --> 00:13:52
 If you personally worship God, you will go to the abode of God.

180
00:13:52 --> 00:13:54
 That is new thing.

181
00:13:54 --> 00:13:58
 These are present everywhere, in every religion.

182
00:13:58 --> 00:14:02
