184
00:14:05 --> 00:14:09
 If you are born in a religion, you die in that same religion.

185
00:14:09 --> 00:14:11
 There is no need of changing the religion.

186
00:14:11 --> 00:14:13
 Paradhamo bhaya vaha.

187
00:14:13 --> 00:14:17
